title: Great Flavor, Authentic, Well Priced
review: This yogurt is my favorite whole milk Greek yogurt.None of the others compare.Amazon Whole Foods also sells it for a great price, good value for the money.Makes a delicious Greek tazikiki (spelling) sauce.Recipe: Chobani whole milk yogurt, shredded cucumber (remove seeds), tablespoon of white vinegar, 3 cloves shredded garlic, 4 or 5 tablespoons of fresh dill, a bit of salt and pepper.Delicious sauce on sandwiches and salmon patties.
